197
00:10:54,920 --> 00:10:56,430
He's so hot.

198
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:08,550
What's that book underneath?

199
00:11:08,550 --> 00:11:09,720
Something I picked up on the way.

200
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:11,360
