206
00:12:21,550 --> 00:12:24,990
I think we should start with theories first.

207
00:12:24,990 --> 00:12:27,160
Are you Lin Jingxiao's spy?

208
00:12:27,160 --> 00:12:29,160
That won't be me.

209
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:33,160
Jingjing is the best!

210
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:34,510
She protects ordinary people!

211
00:12:34,510 --> 00:12:35,750
Those who submit will prosper!

212
00:12:35,750 --> 00:12:38,190
Those who resist shall perish!

213
00:12:40,800 --> 00:12:41,600
Jingjing.

214
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:42,550
Shut up.

215
00:13:14,280 --> 00:13:16,880
My feet are like the golden sword.

216
00:13:17,990 --> 00:13:22,180
They are over 48 inches long, and weigh over 11 pounds.

217
00:13:22,920 --> 00:13:25,250
