257
00:16:35,630 --> 00:16:36,990
Went home.

258
00:16:36,990 --> 00:16:38,430
Relax, I got you.

259
00:16:41,510 --> 00:16:43,240
But you have swimming practice.

260
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:44,240
That's fine.

261
00:16:45,430 --> 00:16:47,040
Give me a moment.

262
00:16:54,280 --> 00:16:56,360
You should keep leaning forward,

263
00:16:56,870 --> 00:16:58,430
